<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa sinah, lawmhnak ka chim lai
 Tuufa cauk chung ka min a tial cang
 A tlau kho lo, a rawk bak lo ding
 Kut hmape in, a ka tial cang.

[C1]
   Bawipa sinah, lawmhnak ka chim lai
   Thangthat raithawinak kan pek Bawipa
   Lunglawmh thawinak, He na sin ka ra
   Sangbik Bawipa, Ka lung a lawm.

[V2]
 Tiva kam ah, Tuufa thlah mi bang
 Ei le din, hni le puan, inn le lo zong
 Nifa tein, hman ding chaw le va
 A ka petu, Bawipa asi.

[V3]
 Bawipa velngeih-nak ka thangthat lai
 Dawp ding thli, mamlo in a ka pek ca
 Ni le thlapa, din awk ti thiang hlim
 A lak tein, a ka hman ter.</lyrics>
<key>E</key>
<title>BAWIPA SINAH LAWMHNAK KA CHIM LAI</title>
</song>